--- n073Z... (how elite is that?!)

after colly 16 i got bummed out and drawing. i did a few requests here and ther
but didn't really start back up until claywar of demonic started doing some
ami/x style mods and working on his bbs, needing art i helped him out. i did
lots of stuff, my new style is a little more developed, but retains the
oldschool ami/x bbs style that everyone in the ascii scene hates now ;) because
this art was for bbses and mods, most of it is colored... some ami/x, some not.
all colored peices were originally going to be included twice, one colored and
one black and white, but i figure it was a cheap way of filling up a colly, but keep in mind that some of the pictures are vastly improved with colors, others
are ruined. if you need anything email me at jp@demonic.net...

-jack phlash (cia/hazmat/demonic)

btw, if some of this work seems rushed, it probably was...





